  <prompt>
    Author the `POST /api/memory/promotions/{id}/reject` Minimal API endpoint per architecture §6.4 + spec FR-32. Tenant-scoped (ADR-008). On call: invokes `IMatterMemoryPromotionService.RejectAsync(id, ct)` (task 093); on success returns 200 with `{ promotionId, status: "rejected" }`; on `not_found` returns 404 ProblemDetails per ADR-019; on `already_resolved` returns 409 ProblemDetails. Event dispatch (`memory.promotion_resolved` with `decision: 'rejected'`) is task 097 work.
  </prompt>

  <role>SPAARKE platform BFF developer. Expert in Minimal API + Spaarke Auth v2 endpoint filters + ProblemDetails error shape.</role>

  <goal>
    Endpoint `POST /api/memory/promotions/{id}/reject` mapped via the `MemoryPromotionEndpoints.cs` file (shared with task 094 — file is already created by 094 OR created here if 094 hasn't landed yet). Tenant scoping enforced. ProblemDetails 404/409 per ADR-019. Integration test covers 200/404/409/cross-tenant/unauthorized matrix. BFF publish-size delta reported. No durable T3 write occurs (architecture §6.4 — reject path is metadata-only).
  </goal>

  <context>
    <background>
      Per architecture §6.4 (promote-to-matter flow — Reject branch posts to this endpoint), spec FR-32. The frontend ContextPane subscriber (task 098) calls this endpoint on user Reject click. Service-side logic in task 093.
    </background>
    <relevant-files>
      <file>src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Memory/MatterMemoryPromotionService.cs (from task 093)</file>
      <file>src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Api/Memory/MemoryPromotionEndpoints.cs (created by 094 or this task)</file>
      <file>src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Program.cs</file>
    </relevant-files>
  </context>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-001">Minimal API `MapPost`.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-008">Tenant scoping via endpoint filter; cross-tenant → 404.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-010">Inject `IMatterMemoryPromotionService` directly.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-013">Endpoint in `Api/Memory/`; service BFF-internal.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-015">Telemetry: endpoint + promotionId + tenantId + decision (`rejected` | `not_found` | `already_resolved`) + durationMs ONLY.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-019">404 + 409 returns ProblemDetails.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-029">≤+0.1 MB delta.</constraint>
    <constraint source="architecture">§6.4 — reject path is metadata-only; no T3 write. Verified at code-review.</constraint>
  </constraints>

